OL,3,CInternet companies could face huge
OL,4,Cfines over content glorifying terrorism
OL,6,FInternet companies will face massive
OL,7,Ffines for hosting content that
OL,8,Fglorifies terrorism, under new powers
OL,9,Ffor the media regulator.
OL,11,FCoimisiun na Mean has been designated
OL,12,Fas the authority to impose the
OL,13,Fpenalties which fall under EU
OL,14,Fregulations.
OL,16,FThe Department of Justice said the
OL,17,Fpowers will provide for "speedy
OL,18,Fremoval of terrorist content online"
OL,19,Fafter gardai issue removal orders.
