OL,6,FJustice Minister Helen McEntee said:
OL,7,F"We have already implemented a number
OL,8,Fof the necessary measures including
OL,9,Fthe designation of An Garda Siochana
OL,10,Fas the competent authority to issue
OL,11,Fremoval orders to online service
OL,12,Fproviders.
OL,14,F"An Garda Siochana plays a vital role
OL,15,Fin this respect and aligns with their
OL,16,Fmission of Keeping People Safe.
